  <title>Tiramisù</title>
  <link>https://lennartwittkuhn.com/recipes/recipes/tiramisu.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 



<div class="callout callout-style-default callout-warning callout-titled">
<div class="callout-header d-flex align-content-center">
<div class="callout-icon-container">
<i class="callout-icon"></i>
</div>
<div class="callout-title-container flex-fill">
Contains raw eggs
</div>
</div>
<div class="callout-body-container callout-body">

</div>
</div>
<section id="fa-basket-shopping-ingredients" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="fa-basket-shopping-ingredients"><i class="fa-solid fa-basket-shopping" aria-label="basket-shopping"></i> Ingredients</h2>
<ul class="task-list">
<li><input type="checkbox">4 fresh eggs</li>
<li><input type="checkbox">100g sugar</li>
<li><input type="checkbox">500g mascarpone</li>
<li><input type="checkbox">Savoiardi (Ladyfingers)</li>
<li><input type="checkbox">Espresso coffee</li>
<li><input type="checkbox">Cocoa powder</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="fa-kitchen-set-procedure" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="fa-kitchen-set-procedure"><i class="fa-solid fa-kitchen-set" aria-label="kitchen-set"></i> Procedure</h2>
<ol type="1">
<li>Put 4 egg yolks and 50g of sugar together, mix them well so they become a bit foamy.</li>
<li>Add 500g mascarpone and mix to make it homogeneous.</li>
<li>Mix 4 egg whites so they become like snow, towards the end add the other 50g of sugar.</li>
<li>Mix the two mixtures together.</li>
<li>Put a thin layer of the cream on the bottom of the tray.</li>
<li>Dip the savoiardi in coffee (don’t make them too soaked as they will soften slowly and if you put too much coffee they become too liquid).</li>
<li>As you dip the savoiardi, place them in the tray.</li>
<li>Cover everything with the rest of the cream.</li>
<li>Sprinkle cocoa powder on top before serving.</li>
</ol>
